data.description: Fantastic Opportunity to own Contemporary Sunny end unit townhouse.  Three stories with ground level family room w/fireplace and door to exterior yard, garage entrance.   Powder room off stairs to main level w Living Room (added electric fireplace), Dining Area, Eat-in-Kitchen w/ Island, desk area, pantry and double doors to deck, Upper-Level w/3 Bedrooms and Double Entry Bath.  Low HOA.  Gleaming Hardwood Floors and recently cleaned carpets. Alarm conveys.  Convenient to Public Transportation and easy access to all parts of DC.  Being Sold in "AS IS" Condition but shows well.
